{"tid":2267172,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"壓力爆煲","createTime":"2020-11-02T01:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T13:38:20.000Z","uid":15516,"like":34,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"be50abe41673218cdb70714a47c2bf14e93ec402","tid":2267172,"uid":15516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:24:30.000Z","msg":"完全係訓唔到覺 每晚失眠<br />\n完全無哂胃口 <br />\n每晚食少少野唔胃痛就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n半工讀都幾撚辛苦<br />\n讀書勁撚多individual 既present 同 project<br />\n返工又跟緊勁撚多project <br />\n又比公事上會接觸既人係咁撚鳩我<br />\n完全做唔撚切 晚晚OT<br />\n又未搵到第份工<br />\n成幾個月都無返過屋企食晚飯<br />\n<br />\n感情上又分左手 生活完全顛覆左<br />\n因為自己而失去左我人生最重視既一個人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n朋友上我都無時間見<br />\n一直都將自己情緒忍住<br />\n一來無地方發洩 <br />\n二來亦都唔好意思影響朋友 要人擔心<br />\n不過好似抑壓得太耐 覺得自己有少少問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b989aba1eef0923eef77a5368499310f87d72e51","tid":2267172,"uid":381041,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:25:36.000Z","msg":"屌過一排無事架啦 咁頹做咩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521c9ee869c914040d11a2b1f5915ae69acce1c1","tid":2267172,"uid":9392,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:26:22.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦屌你老母扮感性 死去隊草啦"},{"pid":"b5250607705aad39cea568b5266fc1485a4a74fd","tid":2267172,"uid":160964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:28:44.000Z","msg":"做下徒手健身<br />\n做完有食欲<br />\n可減壓<br />\n<br />\n建議辭職"},{"pid":"5014f473a26a349d3fb1cbc28cc02cf03312a6b7","tid":2267172,"uid":345392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:35:14.000Z","msg":"永遠都係個心死咗 對方先會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇嘢返到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2284fa43631462d6ba77055dfbad9ed2375808","tid":2267172,"uid":16